---
---
<section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img 
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618843479313-40f8afb4b4d8?q=80&w=2670&auto=format&fit=crop" 
      alt="Autos Velacruz Premium Showcase" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-950 via-zinc-950/80 to-zinc-950"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center pt-20">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-brand/30 bg-brand/10 text-brand text-sm font-medium mb-8">
      <span class="relative flex h-2.5 w-2.5">
        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-brand opacity-75"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-brand"></span>
      </span>
      Tu concesionario premium en Valdemoro
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">
      Encuentra el coche <br />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand to-emerald-400">que mereces</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-12">
      Revisión exhaustiva, transparencia y tratos personalizados. Disfruta de la máxima calidad y confianza en la compra de tu próximo vehículo de ocasión.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/vehiculos-ocasion" class="bg-brand text-zinc-950 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(34,197,94,0.4)]">
        Ver Catálogo
      </a>
      <a href="/compramos-tu-coche" class="bg-zinc-900/80 backdrop-blur border border-zinc-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-zinc-800 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
        Tasar mi coche
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
